`isValid` has been supported in master branch now:
```
    @Override
    public final boolean isValid(final int timeout) throws SQLException {
        for (Connection connection : cachedConnections.values()) {
            if (!connection.isValid(timeout)) {
                return false;
            }
        }
        return true;
    }
```

